Capital One Bank (USA), National Association Key Developments

Capital One Bank Presents at NAREIT Annual Convention, Nov-15-2016
Nov 4 16
Capital One Bank Presents at NAREIT Annual Convention, Nov-15-2016 . Venue: JW Marriott Phoenix Desert Ridge Hotel, Phoenix, Arizona, United States. Speakers: Cameron Daboll, Daniel M. Bernstein, Jonathan Bloomberg.


Capital One Bank Auto Finance Center to Relocate to Eastgate Metroplex
Apr 28 16
Capital One Bank auto finance center to relocate to Eastgate Metroplex. Capital One signed a 10-year lease for 83,069 square feet at the former Dillard's building, 14002 E. 21st St. The new Capital One location will house about 650 associates who provide customer service support at company's auto finance business on the Verizon Cherokee Campus, 6929 N. Lakewood Ave. The business is expected to relocate by the third quarter of 2016.


Capital One Bank Names Tiffany Cason as Fort Worth Market President
Jan 24 16
Capital One Bank named Tiffany Cason as Fort Worth market president and middle market commercial banking executive.


